      <p>A book is so exciting!  At least with the blog posts you can only read over it so many times before you have to press publish &#8211; I can only imagine the temptation that comes with a publication date so far in the future.  Write, read over, rewrite, read over, edit, re-edit, etc.  The frequency with which the blog has to be updated removes that bit of insanity, and I&#8217;m sure provides you with some well-needed grounding every week.  Also &#8211; I&#8217;ve been using dilled creme fraiche in a lot of things too lately, so I was really glad to see it make an appearance here!</p>
